_refine.details                                  
;Individual anisotropic B-factor refinement as implemented in Refmac was performed. 
Reflections to 1.3A resolution (40% of total) are also included in the refinement. The completeness at 1.5A is 97.9%. Crystals were grown at physiological pH.
CNS was also used for refinement.
